<plot>When a Filipino mail order bride arrives in a small town outside of Sydney she becomes aware of cultural differences by way of the inherent sexism and racism of her husband and his mates. She sees the Aboriginal living conditions in the country town as being not too far removed from the country she has left.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?352728</url></doc>
